title Exercise 0.4: New note

browser->server: GET /exampleapp/new_note
server->browser: 302 redirect /exampleapp/notes
browser->server: POST /exampleapp/notes
note right of server: server updates note
server->browser: HTML code
browser->server: GET /exampleapp/main.css
server->browser: main.css
browser->server: GET /exampleapp/main.js
server->browser: main.js
note left of browser: executes main.js
browser->server: GET /exampleapp/data.json
server->browser: data.json
note left of browser: js populates the list with data in data.json
